{"tid":1408010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發)醫護撑罷工","createTime":"2019-08-04T16:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:10:38.000Z","uid":271755,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bf462df358c557c45a9f6ba307b4f580606b59fb","tid":1408010,"uid":271755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"我地係新界西一群關心社會的醫護人員。因職責在身,未能罷工。但我們會在5/8戴上黑色口罩及黑絲帶以示支持。希望政府出來回應港人五大訴求,因為這才是目前香港最逼切的訴求。<br />\n希望其他醫院一起發起黑口罩及黑絲帶行動,於5/8當天配戴,一齊支持香港! <br />\n香港貴在有香港人!<br />\n五大訴求:<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/weoUF3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FweoUF3U.jpg&h=0331305d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aLukBCe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaLukBCe.jpg&h=491c53cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzL703V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzL703V.jpg&h=e43bab13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QOUAqvB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOUAqvB.jpg&h=37d3a0f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jbyWCi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jbyWCi.jpg&h=cbe8d5a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xuu43hj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXuu43hj.jpg&h=e739c66a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f8154ccc4527f80e3fbb8367b37aead44987008","tid":1408010,"uid":259530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b9eb4a27405e2a09f7bf6ffa59f86f94055547","tid":1408010,"uid":267832,"like":0,"dislike":0,